You said:
mujhe online gst 3b file karna hai step by step meri madad kariye himdi me
ChatGPT said:

Bilkul! Main aapko GSTR-3B online file karne ka step-by-step process Hindi me batata hoon. Yeh kaam aap GST Portal (www.gst.gov.in) par kar sakte hain. Dhyan rahe ki aapke paas login ID aur password hona chahiye.

✅ GSTR-3B File Karne ke Liye Jaruri Documents:

  1. Sales aur Purchase ka data (invoice wise)

  2. ITC (Input Tax Credit) ka detail

  3. Nil return ke liye sirf login karna hoga, invoice nahi chahiye

🔁 Step-by-Step Process (Hindi Me):

STEP 1: GST Portal Par Login Karen

  • Website: https://www.gst.gov.in

  • “Login” par click karein

  • Apna Username, Password aur Captcha bhar kar login karein

STEP 2: Return Dashboard Open Karen

  • Login ke baad “Returns Dashboard” par click karein

  • Apna financial year aur month select karein (jaise MAY 2025)

STEP 3: GSTR-3B Form Select Karen

  • “Prepare Online” par click karein GSTR-3B ke samne

STEP 4: Form Fill Karen (Ek Ek Section Me)

4.1 – Details of Outward Supplies (Sales)

  • Taxable outward supplies (B2C/B2B) ka amount aur tax bharein

4.2 – Inter-state supplies to unregistered persons

  • Agar kisi doosre rajya me B2C sale hai to uska detail yahan bharein

4.3 – Eligible ITC (Input Tax Credit)

  • Purchase invoices se milne wale ITC ka detail bharein (IGST, CGST, SGST)

4.4 – Ineligible ITC

  • Agar koi ITC claim nahi kar sakte to uska bhi mention karein

4.5 – Interest and Late Fee

  • Agar delay hua hai to interest/late fee yahan bharein (portal auto-calculate karta hai)

STEP 5: Payment of Tax

  • “Payment of Tax” section me available cash/credit ledger show hoga

  • Tax liability adjust karen

  • Agar cash pay karna hai to “Create Challan” par click karke net banking se payment karen

STEP 6: Preview & Verify

  • “Preview Draft GSTR-3B” par click karke sabhi detail ek baar check karein

  • Agar sab theek hai to Submit button dabayein

STEP 7: Final File Karna

  • Submit hone ke baad “File GSTR-3B with EVC/DSC” par click karein

  • Aapko OTP aayega (mobile/email) – use enter karke return file ho jayega

🧾 Filing ke Baad:

  • Aapko Acknowledgment Reference Number (ARN) milega

  • File hone ke baad aap “Return Filed” status dekh sakte hain

🆘 Agar aapne purchase bills bheje hain:

Mujhe sirf yeh batayein:

  • Aapka GSTIN

  • Kis month ka return hai (jaise MAY 2025)

  • ITC lena hai ya NIL return hai?

Main aapka GSTR-3B data Excel format me bana kar de sakta hoon.

Aap chahein to:
📤 Google Drive ya 📧 Email se apne invoice images bhej sakte hain.

Aap ready hain to shuru karte hain.
